name: Cellfish Power
description:
CELLFISH POWER

You become your own power by draining your life out of you! Pay what you want to make yourself stronger but beware because once there is no more of you, you are done!

HOW TO PLAY

 XBOX controller:

  • Stick to move
  •  A to attack

Keyboard controller:

  • WASD to move
  • E to attack
